[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0878","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0878.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0599","title":"通用 网络入侵检测系统 TCP异常序列号绕过检测漏洞","description":"网络入侵检测系统（IDS）在处理包含异常TCP序列号的数据包时存在逻辑缺陷，攻击者可通过向目标网络发送精心构造的异常序列号数据包绕过IDS的检测与重组机制，导致恶意流量无法被正确识别和告警。该漏洞影响多种主流IDS产品，攻击者无需认证即可远程实施绕过攻击，严重削弱网络安全监控与威胁检测的有效性。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0599"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.620","remediation":"升级支持 TCP 流重组（stream reassembly）的入侵检测系统，如 Suricata、Zeek（原名 Bro），并启用 `stream.reassembly` 引擎；禁用纯包级检测的旧式 IDS（如 Snort 1.x 传统模式）。配置 IDS 确保 TCP 分片重组策略与受保护目标主机一致（如设置 `target-based` 策略），避免插包（insertion）和逃逸（evasion）攻击。定期更新检测规则集以覆盖已知逃逸技术。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.robertgraham.com/mirror/Ptacek-Newsham-Evasion-98.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0599.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0599","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0599.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0599.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0599.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cgq4-92x7-335m/GHSA-cgq4-92x7-335m.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0599.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86252/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0878.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0879","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0879.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0600","title":"网络入侵检测系统 数据包校验和未验证漏洞","description":"网络入侵检测系统（IDS）在处理网络数据包时未验证校验和字段的正确性，远程攻击者可通过发送精心构造的畸形数据包绕过 IDS 的检测规则。由于 IDS 与目标主机对数据包的解析结果不一致，攻击者可利用该缺陷隐藏恶意流量，实现绕过告警的入侵行为。该漏洞影响多数未实现校验和验证的 IDS 产品，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0600"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.743","remediation":"在 IDS/IPS 配置中启用 IP 和 TCP 校验和验证功能（如 Snort 的 `config checksum_mode: all`），丢弃校验和错误的报文；升级至支持完整校验和检测的现代 IDS 版本（如 Suricata 7.x 或 Snort 3.x）；在边界防火墙上启用 TCP 校验和强制检查；同时在网络设备上启用 IP 选项过滤和分片重组校验，消除攻击者利用校验和绕过检测的路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.robertgraham.com/mirror/Ptacek-Newsham-Evasion-98.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0600.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0600","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0600.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0600.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0600.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9m27-cjg7-pj49/GHSA-9m27-cjg7-pj49.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0600.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86246/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0879.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0880","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0880.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0601","title":"通用 网络入侵检测系统 TCP握手数据绕过漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0601 为网络入侵检测系统（IDS）中存在的TCP数据包处理缺陷。攻击者可在TCP三次握手过程中，将恶意载荷嵌入SYN、SYN-ACK等握手数据包的载荷字段或利用IP分片重组绕过IDS的深度包检测机制。由于早期IDS对TCP会话建立阶段的数据包缺乏完整重组与检测能力，导致攻击载荷可绕过安全审计直接到达目标主机。该漏洞影响了多种主流IDS产品的检测有效性，攻击者无需认证即可实施绕过，危害网络层面的安全监控体系。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0601"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.863","remediation":"启用 IDS/IPS 的 TCP 流重组功能（如 Snort 的 stream_tcp 预处理器或 Suricata 的内置流引擎），配置为自动重组所有 TCP 会话的完整载荷后再进行规则匹配；同时启用 TCP 规范化（normalization）以丢弃重叠分片或异常标志位的数据包，防止分片逃逸攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.robertgraham.com/mirror/Ptacek-Newsham-Evasion-98.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0601.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0601","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0601.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0601.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0601.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-45cf-cf6g-j6mm/GHSA-45cf-cf6g-j6mm.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0601.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86244/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0880.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0881","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0881.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0602","title":"多厂商网络入侵检测系统IP碎片重组绕过检测漏洞","description":"网络入侵检测系统（IDS）在处理碎片化IP数据包时存在重组缺陷，攻击者可通过发送特制的碎片数据包绕过IDS检测规则。由于IDS无法正确还原原始载荷，恶意流量被误判为正常，导致攻击行为逃逸检测。该漏洞影响多种主流IDS产品，远程攻击者无需认证即可利用，且攻击复杂度低，无需用户交互。利用方式包括发送超小碎片、重叠偏移或超时碎片等绕过技术。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0602"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.983","remediation":"升级 IDS/IPS 引擎至最新版本（如 Snort ≥2.9.20、Suricata ≥7.0），启用 frag3 预处理器的分片重组功能；配置 `preprocessor frag3_global: max_frags 65536` 和 `preprocessor frag3_engine: policy windows`；对于无法升级的旧版系统，在网络层启用分片包拦截策略，仅允许完整 IP 包进入检测引擎。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.robertgraham.com/mirror/Ptacek-Newsham-Evasion-98.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0602.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0602","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0602.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0602.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0602.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8cxh-9x8c-5qr7/GHSA-8cxh-9x8c-5qr7.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0602.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86251/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0881.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0882","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0882.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0603","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 用户组成员权限配置不当漏洞","description":"在 Windows NT 系统中，用户账户可能被不当添加到高权限用户组（如 Administrators、Backup Operators、Domain Admins 等），导致低权限用户意外获得超出预期的系统访问权限。该漏洞源于系统组策略配置缺陷或管理失误，攻击者可利用已获取的低权限账户通过提权操作完全控制目标系统，影响 Windows NT 4.0 及更早版本。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0603"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:43.093","remediation":"立即审查所有域控制器和成员服务器上 Administrators、Backup Operators、Domain Admins、Power Users 等高权限组的成员列表，移除非必要或未授权的用户账户。通过「管理工具 → 计算机管理 → 本地用户和组 → 组」逐一检查各组成员，确保仅保留最小必要权限。部署安全基线策略（如 Microsoft Security Compliance Toolkit），定期审计组成员变更日志，并启用 Windows 审核策略中的「组成员管理」事件审计。升级至 Windows Server 2003 或更高版本以利用细化的权限委派机制（如委派控制向导），避免将普通用户加入内置特权组。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0603","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0603.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0603.json","https://github.com/CVEDB/Poc-Git/blob/0275aeb329b0747c9a1d46160c921eae06095557/1999/CVE-1999-0603.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0603.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0603.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0603","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0603.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0603.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0603.md","https://github.com/brenonevs/prs-pentest/blob/001cf17eedeb4aad73618d3140ca1f5dc93e69b3/CVEs & POCs/1999/CVE-1999-0603.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0882.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0891","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0891.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0611","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 注册表键值配置不当漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统中存在关键注册表项权限配置不当的安全漏洞。该漏洞允许远程攻击者利用不恰当的注册表键值，在目标系统上执行未授权操作，可能导致系统信息泄露、权限提升或拒绝服务。由于受影响注册表项涉及系统核心功能，攻击者一旦利用成功可完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响了 Windows NT 4.0 等早期版本，危害等级为严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0611"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:44.057","remediation":"检查注册表键 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\ 下关键子键的值权限，将不当值修改为默认安全配置；同时安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a 及后续安全更新，限制对注册表的远程访问权限，仅允许授权管理员通过 ACL 进行修改。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0611","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0611.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0611.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0611","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0611.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0611.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0611.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0611.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86267/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0891.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0894","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0894.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0613","title":"Sun RPC rpc.sprayd 服务本地权限提升漏洞","description":"rpc.sprayd 是 Unix 系统中用于网络喷发测试的 RPC 服务，运行于 100012 端口。由于 sprayd 守护进程以 root 权限运行且未对调用来源进行充分权限校验，本地攻击者可通过发送特制的 RPC 请求触发 sprayd 命令执行，将自身权限提升至 root。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris、HP-UX 及其他运行 rpc.sprayd 服务的类 Unix 系统，攻击者需拥有目标系统的本地 shell 访问权限。建议在非必要环境下禁用该服务或配置 RPC 访问控制列表。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0613"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:44.303","remediation":"立即禁用 rpc.sprayd 服务：在 Solaris 中执行 `svcadm disable svc:/network/rpc/spray:default` 或从 inetd.conf 中注释 sprayd 行并重启 inetd。同时配置防火墙/TCP Wrapper 限制 RPC 端口（111/32771-32800）仅允许可信网段访问，并安装操作系统厂商提供的 RPC 安全补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0613","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0613.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0613.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0613","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0613.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0613.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0613.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0613.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83127/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0894.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0895","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0895.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0614","title":"通用 FTP 服务运行配置问题","description":"CVE-1999-0614 候选编号已被官方拒绝使用。该条目原始描述仅指出 FTP 服务正在运行，属于系统配置管理范畴，而非独立的安全漏洞。此类配置问题更适合在通用配置枚举（CCE）框架中收录，不具备传统的攻击向量、利用条件或安全影响。因此该编号不应被用于描述任何安全缺陷，也不构成对系统机密性、完整性和可用性的直接威胁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0614"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.310","remediation":"如非业务必要，建议关闭 FTP 服务（systemctl disable vsftpd/proftpd 或移除对应软件包）；如必须使用，应替换为 SFTP/FTPS 等加密传输协议，并配置防火墙仅允许受信 IP 访问（如 iptables -A INPUT -p tcp --dport 21 -s 信任网段 -j ACCEPT），同时限制匿名登录、禁用 root 账户直接 FTP 登录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0614.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0614","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0614.json","https://github.com/scipag/AttackToolKit/blob/78bf88564956b8f18a37659dc3d345093e95a136/plugins/FTP%20server%20detection.plugin","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0614.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000451.txt","https://github.com/athiasjerome/XORCISM/blob/327e2a3be196660f82c89ae9d7c4e7abe4785b0d/SOURCES/XProviderQualys/QualysSampleResults.xml","https://github.com/Planet-Source-Code/marc-ruef-attack-tool-kit-3-0__1-57240/blob/96061f959b3cf8ad81fa5d603944798cc9f3304c/atk-3.0src/plugins/Macintosh%20OS%20X%20FTP%20server%20detection.plugin"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0895.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0896","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0896.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0615","title":"SNMP 服务配置不当漏洞","description":"SNMP 服务在未配置访问控制或使用默认团体字符串时运行，远程攻击者可通过网络探测 UDP 端口 161/162 获取系统信息，包括网络拓扑、运行进程、系统配置和用户账户等敏感数据。该条目已被 NVD 拒绝，理由是此问题属于配置枚举范畴（CCE）而非直接安全漏洞，CVSS 为 0。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0615"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.343","remediation":"如非必要，建议在系统服务中禁用 SNMP 服务 (snmpd)，减少攻击面。如需使用 SNMP，应升级至支持 SNMPv3 的版本并启用认证与加密（配置 authPriv），同时通过防火墙限制 UDP 161/162 端口的访问来源 IP，仅允许受信任的管理端连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0615.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0615","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0615.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0615.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/Felix-sec/VulnDataExtr/blob/1f4ecda04291a8a4eb7e49189a9ee2bc026b8389/exact_keywords.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0615.json","https://github.com/aboutcode-org/aboutcode-mirror-euvd/blob/1b758e4b71978ff973a6df1bc69fc70b932735fb/advisories/2000/02/EUVD-1999-0598.json","https://github.com/Software-Engineering-2026-Class/kelompok4-cyber-kg-agentic/blob/0fc3a7d1e2416617ef834c956997e1f0f283424b/parser_agent/output/cve.ttl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0896.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0899","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0899.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0616","title":"TFTP 服务开放导致信息泄露风险","description":"该CVE条目已被官方驳回（REJECT），原描述为\"TFTP服务正在运行\"。TFTP协议使用UDP 69端口，缺乏认证与加密机制，若未配置适当访问控制，运行中的TFTP服务可能被未经授权的攻击者利用进行文件读写操作，导致敏感信息泄露或任意文件上传。但由于该问题属于安全配置范畴而非代码层面的直接安全漏洞，因此不适用CVE编号体系，更适合归入CCE（通用配置枚举）管理。建议在非必要环境中禁用TFTP服务或限制访问来源。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0616"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.373","remediation":"若业务不需要 TFTP 服务，建议在系统中停止并禁用 tftpd/tftp-hpa 服务（如 `systemctl disable tftp` 或移除 xinetd 配置）。如需使用，通过 iptables/firewalld 限制源 IP 访问 UDP 端口 69，仅允许受信任的管理网段连接，并考虑迁移至 SFTP/SCP 等加密文件传输协议。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0616.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0616","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0616.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/tftpd_detect.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0616.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000453.txt","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/tftpd_detect.nasl","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0616.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0899.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0904","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0904.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0618","title":"Unix rexec 服务权限提升漏洞","description":"rexec（远程执行）服务是一种未加密的远程命令执行协议，运行在 TCP 512 端口，使用主机名和 .rhosts 文件进行基于主机的认证。攻击者可通过伪造信任主机 IP 地址或利用 .rhosts 配置缺陷绕过认证，在目标系统上以当前用户权限执行任意命令，实现权限提升。该服务默认不启用加密，明文传输密码，容易被中间人攻击窃听。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，建议禁用 rexec 服务并改用 SSH。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0618"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:44.510","remediation":"立即禁用 rexec 服务（通常为 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释 exec 行或 systemctl stop rexec），并使用 SSH（OpenSSH）替代所有远程执行需求。检查系统是否仍在运行 rexecd/in.rexecd 进程并予以停止卸载。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0618","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0618.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0618","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0618.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0618.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0618.json","https://github.com/DefectDojo/django-DefectDojo/blob/619e5656f308396a3cc3a7f039c6426ae98baa17/unittests/scans/openvas/many_vuln.xml","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/rexecd.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jw99-fq4j-hx93/GHSA-jw99-fq4j-hx93.json","https://github.com/ornl-sava/nv/blob/8cbf2a775f3c35accff96fe30217e9afff65410e/data/metasploitable.2.0.nbe","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0618.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0904.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0907","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0907.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0619","title":"通用 Telnet 服务配置不当问题","description":"该候选编号已被拒绝，原描述为\"Telnet 服务正在运行\"。Telnet 协议以明文传输所有数据（包括用户名和密码），未提供任何加密或认证机制，远程攻击者可通过网络嗅探拦截并窃取敏感凭据。此条目属于安全配置问题（不应启用不安全的 Telnet 服务）而非软件漏洞，因此被移入通用配置枚举（CCE）进行管理，建议使用 SSH 等安全替代方案。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0619"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.450","remediation":"关闭 Telnet 服务（端口 23），改用 SSH（端口 22）进行远程管理。如因兼容性无法禁用，应在防火墙限制 Telnet 的源 IP 访问范围，仅允许受信任的管理网段连接，并启用加密通道（如 stunnel）封装 Telnet 流量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0619.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0619","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0619.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0619.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/harshsingh4469/endpoint-security-analyzer/blob/39935d29fd093a995963ab16d1953b9224b57717/scanner.py","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000455.txt","https://github.com/SwethaV0611/Network_vuln/blob/fce59788552720e2cf78ee52ee7c584a9475da61/scanner/vulnerability.py","https://github.com/athiasjerome/XORCISM/blob/327e2a3be196660f82c89ae9d7c4e7abe4785b0d/SOURCES/XProviderQualys/QualysSampleResults.xml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0907.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0910","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0910.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0620","title":"NIS 相关服务运行配置问题","description":"该漏洞编号已被 NVD 驳回，原描述为目标系统上运行了 NIS（Network Information System）组件服务。NIS 协议在设计上缺乏加密和认证机制，通过网络在局域网内传输用户账户数据（包括密码哈希）时，处于同一网段的攻击者可进行网络嗅探，捕获 NIS 映射数据后实施离线破解，进而获取系统访问权限。该问题属于安全配置核查范畴，并非传统代码层面的安全漏洞，广泛影响启用 NIS 服务的 Unix/Linux 系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0620"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.480","remediation":"如业务无需 NIS 服务，应停止 ypserv/ypbind 服务并设置开机不自启：systemctl disable --now ypserv ypbind。如确需使用 NIS，应在 /var/yp/securenets 中限定仅允许受信任子网访问，并避免与互联网直连。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0620.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0620","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0620.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0620.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0620.json","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv","https://github.com/Software-Engineering-2026-Class/kelompok4-cyber-kg-agentic/blob/0fc3a7d1e2416617ef834c956997e1f0f283424b/parser_agent/output/cve.ttl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0910.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0912","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0912.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0621","title":"Various vendors NETBIOS 组件服务配置不当","description":"该候选编号已被拒绝。原条目仅描述 NETBIOS 相关组件服务处于运行状态，属于安全配置范畴而非可直接引入安全漏洞的缺陷。此类配置问题更适合由通用配置枚举（CCE）覆盖管理，因此该 CVE 编号作废，建议参考 CCE 标准进行安全配置检查。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0621"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.540","remediation":"禁用 NetBIOS over TCP/IP：在网络连接属性中取消选中\"Microsoft 网络的文件和打印机共享\"的绑定，或在高级 TCP/IP 设置中禁用 NetBIOS。在防火墙层面，阻止外部访问 UDP 137-138 和 TCP 139、445 端口。如业务不需要，直接停止 Server 服务并禁用 SMBv1。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0621.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0621","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0621.json","htt